ses/phase-12.md)\n\nRequirements:\n- Shutdown operation stops accepting new tasks\n- Adding tasks after shutdown = error\n- Wait for processing tasks up to configurable timeout\n- Force-cancel if timeout exceeded\n- Register callbacks to run during shutdown\n- Return shutdown summary (completed, cancelled, duration)\n- Multiple shutdown calls safe\n- Immediate completion if no processing tasks\n\n### 8. Source Code Status\n\n**The `/workspace/src/` directory is currently empty** (contains only `.gitkeep`). All implementation needs to be created.\n\n### 9. Test Configuration Files\n\n**vitest.config.ts** is configured with:\n- `globals: true` -- global test functions available\n- `testTimeout: 10000` -- 10 second timeout per test\n\nNo other test configuration files present. Tests should be written using Vitest.\n\nThis is a comprehensive greenfield project where you need to implement a complete 12-phase task queue system from scratch, starting with the basic FIFO queue in Phase 1 and building incrementally toward a sophisticated system with middleware, scheduling, and graceful shutdown by Phase 12."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a87bfe1 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 22571\ntool_uses: 22\nduration_ms: 35343</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"559f85dd-1303-46a3-8972-9b29b427318f","uuid":"7e04f24a-6521-4cae-a963-3d213e477576","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Thoroughly explore the entire codebase. I need:\n1. The full directory structure\n2. Contents of package.json, tsconfig.json, any config files\n3. Contents of TASK.md\n4. Contents of ALL files in the phases/ directory (phases/*.md) - every single one\n5. Contents of any existing files in src/\n6. Contents of any test configuration files\n7. The eslint configuration\n\nBe very thorough - read every phase file completely.","agentId":"a87bfe1","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have completed a thorough exploration of the c